thread.title: CRYSTAL
thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by CRYSTAL

author: CRYSTAL
title: CRYSTAL
text: I've been using American Frame since I was in high school. Even after moving away, I continued to order my frames through them because of their excellent service, quality, and low prices. Now that I'm teaching in a high school, they are the only company I will order from for framing supplies for my students. Ordering and delivering to my school were a breeze. They've never let me down.
